class Solution:
    def findMin(self, nums: List[int]) -> int:
        def dfs(l, r):
            if l > r:
                return None
            i = l + (r-l)//2
            x = nums[i]
            if i >= len(nums) or x < nums[i-1] or x > nums[i+1]:
                return nums[i]
            return dfs(l, i-1) + nums[i] - dfs(i+1, r)
        return dfs(0, len(nums)-1)
